title: Heavy rain and storms tipped for Australia's south-east in wake of ideal Easter weather
description: A cold front moving through Victoria, New South Wales and Tasmania is expected to be followed by heavy rain, storms and potentially the first east coast low for 2024.
content:
This week will deliver heavy rain to much of eastern Australia.
